components.content: You need to help Farmer Lucy stop the elephants from entering the farm.
There are 3 ways you can do this:
Add beehives around the corn crops.
The elephants will see the beehives and be scared away.
Plant cotton crops around the corn crops to attract bees.
​​​​​​​The bees will scare away the elephants.
fence. The barbs will hurt the elephants and stop them from entering the farm.
